# Implementation Summary - Complete System

## Project Overview
**Store Parts Management System** - A complete machinery parts inward entry system with master data management and dropdown integration.

## ? What's Complete

### 1. Database Schema ?
- **machinery_item_inward_unit2** - Main transaction table
- **PartyMaster** - Party/vendor master data
- **ItemMaster** - Item/part master data
- All tables with proper relationships and constraints

### 2. Master Forms ?

#### PartyMasterForm
- ? Add, Edit, Delete, Clear functionality
- ? Validation (party_name required)
- ? Active/Inactive toggle
- ? Contact person, phone, address fields
- ? DataGridView with all parties
- ? Record counter
- ? Double-click to edit
- ? Confirmation on delete

#### ItemMasterForm
- ? Add, Edit, Delete, Clear functionality
- ? Validation (item_name required)
- ? Active/Inactive toggle
- ? Item code, description, unit fields
- ? DataGridView with all items
- ? Record counter
- ? Double-click to edit
- ? Confirmation on delete

### 3. Main Form (Form1) ?
- ? Complete transaction entry form
- ? **Party Name** - Dropdown with active parties
- ? **Item** - Dropdown with active items
- ? All transaction fields (challan no, dates, qty, etc.)
- ? Add New, Save, Clear buttons
- ? Validation before save
- ? Auto-increment ID handling
- ? Integration with master forms

### 4. ShowTableForm ?
- ? View all transaction data in grid
- ? Edit capabilities
- ? Search/filter functionality
- ? Refresh data

### 5. Dropdown Integration ?
- ? Party Name ComboBox with master data
- ? Item ComboBox with master data
- ? Filter for active items only
- ? AutoComplete support
- ? Data binding to main table
- ? Validation (required fields)
- ? Auto-refresh after adding new master data

## ?? Complete File List

### Core Application Files
```
store parts/
