## ?? Technical Architecture

### Data Binding Structure
```
MainDB.xsd (Dataset)
    ?
    ??? machinery_item_inward_unit2 Table
    ?   ??? machinery_item_inward_unit2TableAdapter
    ?   ??? machinery_item_inward_unit2BindingSource
    ?       ??? Form1 Controls
    ?           ??? idTextBox
    ?           ??? challan_noTextBox
    ?           ??? dateDateTimePicker
    ?           ??? party_nameComboBox ? Bound to party_name
    ?           ??? itemComboBox ? Bound to item
    ?           ??? ... other fields
    ?
    ??? PartyMaster Table
    ?   ??? PartyMasterTableAdapter
    ?   ??? partyMasterBindingSource (Filter: is_active = true)
    ?       ??? party_nameComboBox (DataSource)
    ?       ??? PartyMasterForm Controls
    ?
    ??? ItemMaster Table
        ??? ItemMasterTableAdapter
        ??? itemMasterBindingSource (Filter: is_active = true)
            ??? itemComboBox (DataSource)
            ??? ItemMasterForm Controls
```

### Form Interaction Flow
```
Form1 (Main Entry)
    ?
    ??? [Manage Parties] Click
    ?   ??? Opens PartyMasterForm
    ?       ??? Add/Edit Parties
    ?           ??? Close
    ?               ??? RefreshMasterData()
    ?                   ??? party_nameComboBox updates ?
    ?
    ??? [Manage Items] Click
    ?   ??? Opens ItemMasterForm
    ?       ??? Add/Edit Items
    ?           ??? Close
    ?               ??? RefreshMasterData()
    ?                   ??? itemComboBox updates ?
    ?
    ??? [Show All Data] Click
        ??? Opens ShowTableForm
            ??? View/Edit Transactions
                ??? Close
                    ??? Refresh main form data ?
```

