## ?? Data Quality Improvements

### Before Implementation
```
Data Issues:
? Typos: "ABC Comapny", "Bareing", "Bol t"
? Duplicates: "ABC Co.", "ABC Company", "ABC Corp"
? Inconsistent: Different spellings each time
? Invalid: Non-existent parties/items
? Cleanup: Required monthly data cleaning

Data Quality: 60-70%
```

### After Implementation
```
Data Quality:
? No typos: Dropdown selection only
? No duplicates: Unique master data
? Consistent: Same name every time
? Valid: Only real parties/items
? Clean: No cleanup needed

Data Quality: 100%
```

## ?? Data Integrity

### Enforced Rules
1. **Party Name:** Must be selected from dropdown (validated)
2. **Item:** Must be selected from dropdown (validated)
3. **ID:** Auto-increment (cannot be manually changed)
4. **Active Status:** Only active items appear in dropdowns
5. **Data Binding:** Changes automatically saved to correct fields

### Data Protection
- Read-only ID field (no manual editing)
- Validation before save
- Confirmation on delete
- Historical data preserved (even if party/item inactive)
- Transaction integrity maintained

