## ?? Support Information

### Getting Help
1. Check relevant documentation files
2. Review error messages carefully
3. Verify master data exists
4. Ensure database connectivity
5. Check Active status on master records

### Common Issues & Solutions
| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| Empty dropdowns | Add data via Manage Parties/Items |
| Can't save | Check validation - select party and item |
| New item not showing | Verify is_active = true in master form |
| Dropdown not refreshing | Close and reopen main form |

